<view class="page">
  <text class="eyebrow">账户与合规</text>
  <text class="title">主体信息、规则与客服</text>
  <text class="subtitle">这里集中展示经营主体、隐私数据说明、内容安全规则和投诉入口。</text>

  <view class="card-list">
    <view
      wx:for="{{sections}}"
      wx:key="title"
      class="card"
      data-url="{{item.url}}"
      bindtap="openSection"
    >
      <text class="card-title">{{item.title}}</text>
      <text class="card-desc">{{item.desc}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
